Require agentgrep

Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-grep.gif
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-grep.mp4
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-grep.webm

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 300
Source docs/_static/demos/vhs/_preamble.tape

Sleep 1s
Type "agentgrep grep -i timeout"
Enter
Wait
Sleep 3s
